<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>纽约时报 &amp;gt; 美国 &amp;gt; 政治</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/spotlight/on-politics</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 28 Apr 2026 15:54:46 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>从州长竞选到财富税提案，亿万富翁正在主导加州政治</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/27/us/politics/california-billionaires-tax-governor.html</link><description>在谢尔盖·布林（Sergey Brin）和汤姆·斯泰尔（Tom Steyer）之间，超级富豪正在努力引导国家的方向。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Apr 2026 21:49:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/27/us/politics/california-billionaires-tax-governor.html</guid></item><item><title>中期选举临近时共和党可能采取的策略：负面竞选</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/24/us/politics/republicans-midterms-campaign.html</link><description>共和党人可能会在中期选举中采取一种久经考验的策略：采取消极态度。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Apr 2026 21:39:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/24/us/politics/republicans-midterms-campaign.html</guid></item><item><title>为什么弗吉尼亚州的新地图对民主党中期选举很重要，以及下一步是什么</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/22/us/politics/virginia-redistricting-map-democrats-midterms.html</link><description>现在注意力转向佛罗里达州和最高法院。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 21:00:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/22/us/politics/virginia-redistricting-map-democrats-midterms.html</guid></item><item><title>民主党人曾经痛恨不公正地划分选区。现在他们正在努力争取。</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/20/us/politics/virginia-gerrymandering-referendum.html</link><description>该党在弗吉尼亚州寻求额外优势之际，该党在绘制政治地图上的党派思维发生了变化——领导人表示，这在很大程度上是因为特朗普总统的策略。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Apr 2026 21:26:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/20/us/politics/virginia-gerrymandering-referendum.html</guid></item><item><title>缅因州选民在 2026 年参议院选举前的想法</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/17/us/politics/maine-senate-election-collins-platner-mills.html</link><description>该州的读者向我们讲述了该州高风险的参议院竞选。</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Apr 2026 22:40:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/17/us/politics/maine-senate-election-collins-platner-mills.html</guid></item><item><title>特朗普和共和党人能收回有关经济的信息吗？</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/15/us/politics/trump-taxes-economy-iran-war.html</link><description>今天是纳税日，但该国的大部分注意力都集中在一场不受欢迎的战争上。</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Apr 2026 21:31:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/15/us/politics/trump-taxes-economy-iran-war.html</guid></item><item><title>埃里克·斯瓦尔韦尔下台后加州州长竞选会发生什么？</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/13/us/politics/swalwell-california-governor.html</link><description>对于民主党人来说，这出戏的影响远远超出了州内范围。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Apr 2026 22:20:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/13/us/politics/swalwell-california-governor.html</guid></item><item><title>2028 年民主党可能的候选人已经在争取黑人选民的支持</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/10/us/politics/black-voters-democrats-2028.html</link><description>可能的总统候选人已经在争取重要的民主党选区。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 Apr 2026 21:32:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/10/us/politics/black-voters-democrats-2028.html</guid></item><item><title>谁为 2026 年中期选举提供资金？很多钱都无法追踪。</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/08/us/politics/midterms-elections-funding-pac.html</link><description>流入政治体系的大量资金最终无法追踪。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Apr 2026 22:21:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/08/us/politics/midterms-elections-funding-pac.html</guid></item><item><title>佛罗里达州的选区重划战争、佐治亚州的决选和最新的政治新闻</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/06/us/politics/redistricting-virginia-florida-ga-special-election-republicans.html</link><description>随着未来两周最后期限的临近，两者都没有完全按照党派计划进行。</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Apr 2026 21:54:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/06/us/politics/redistricting-virginia-florida-ga-special-election-republicans.html</guid></item></channel></rss>